# Team 1: Explorer — Website Redesign
# Lead: Conductor | v0.18.3 | 27 March 2026
#
# CENTER OF GRAVITY (defined by Conductor):
# "Recipients land on sgraph.ai and become senders.
#  The site must show the product, prove the privacy, and convert curiosity to action.
#  We measure success by: a recipient can land, understand, and click Try Free
#  in under 90 seconds — without reading a word of copy if the screenshots are right."
#
# TEAM COMPOSITION
# Role         | Scope
# Conductor    | Orchestrates, monitors workstream blockers, owns decisions
# Sherpa       | All copy — hero, sections, /why/ pages, /security/ depth
# Designer     | All layouts — two-column hero, screenshot rows, cards, mobile
# Architect    | Claim verification, schema markup, SEO, migration risk
# Ambassador   | Competitive table, launch copy, social posts
# Developer    | HTML/CSS/JS build across all phases
# Librarian    | Issues-FS maintenance, reality doc updates, devpack updates
